prompts.frontCover:
A beautiful 2D flat illustration for a greeting card front. In the center, Lao Lao (woman from the photo) and Jordan (man from the photo) are illustrated as cartoon characters, sitting happily on a large, comfy beach blanket on soft sand. Lao Lao is wearing her light blue sweatshirt and black pants. Jordan is wearing his tan hoodie and dark pants. Lao Lao has a big, delighted smile as she holds up a comically large birthday bone treat, tied with a pretty ribbon, towards the viewer. Jordan is laughing beside her, arm around her shoulder, pointing at the bone. In front of them on the blanket sits an adorable, small, fluffy white dog (representing Jordan, the sender) wearing a tiny party hat, looking up at Lao Lao with an adoring expression and its tail wagging excitedly.

The scene is framed by a beautiful botanical border composed of lush, tropical foliage like monstera leaves, palm fronds, and delicate hibiscus flowers, all in soft watercolor textures. The beach background is serene with gentle, light blue ocean waves and a clear sky. Scattered around the blanket are fun beach elements: a half-eaten birthday cake for humans with one candle, a couple of seashells, and a dog's water bowl.

In the upper center of the card, floating gracefully above the couple, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color. The overall style is lighthearted, vibrant, and full of warmth and humor.
